content: I'm actually considering getting into sprouted grain wraps for my lunchbox sandwiches. I've been trying to cut down on carbs, and I've heard sprouted grain wraps can be a good option. By the way, speaking of lunchbox sandwiches, I usually make a turkey and avocado sandwich with carrot sticks and hummus, and I was wondering if you could suggest some other healthy accompaniments that would go well with my meal?
